<div class="NavFrame collapsed" style="border: none; padding: 0;">
<div class="NavHead" style="font-size: 105%; background: transparent; text-align: left; text-align:left;;">Philosophy and history of science</div>
<div class="NavContent" style="font-size: 105%; padding: 0.2em 0 0.4em; text-align: center;">
<ul>
<li><a href="History_of_science" title="History of science">History of science</a></li>
<li><a href="Philosophy_of_science" title="Philosophy of science">Philosophy of science</a></li>
<li><a href="Science_policy" title="Science policy">Science policy</a></li>
<li><strong class="selflink">Scientific method</strong></li>
<li><a href="Fringe_science" title="Fringe science">Fringe science</a></li>
<li><a href="Pseudoscience" title="Pseudoscience">Pseudoscience</a></li>
<li><a href="Technoscience" title="Technoscience">Technoscience</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class="" style="padding:0.3em 0.4em 0.3em;font-weight:bold;border-top: 1px solid #aaa; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa;">
