<li><a href="../Arthur_W._Burks" title="Arthur W. Burks" class="mw-redirect">Burks, Arthur W.</a>, <i>Chance, Cause, Reason — An Inquiry into the Nature of Scientific Evidence</i>, University of Chicago Press, Chicago, IL, 1977.</li>
