<li><a href="John_Earman" title="John Earman">Earman, John</a> (ed.), <i>Inference, Explanation, and Other Frustrations: Essays in the Philosophy of Science</i>, University of California Press, Berkeley &amp; Los Angeles, CA, 1992.</li>
