<li><a href="../../w/index-title=Cheryl_J._Misak&action=edit&redlink=1.php.html" class="new" title="Cheryl J. Misak (page does not exist)">Misak, Cheryl J.</a>, <i>Truth and the End of Inquiry, A Peircean Account of Truth</i>, Oxford University Press, Oxford, UK, 1991.</li>
<li><a href="../../w/index-title=Massimo_Piattelli-Palmarini&action=edit&redlink=1.php.html" class="new" title="Massimo Piattelli-Palmarini (page does not exist)">Piattelli-Palmarini, Massimo</a> (ed.), <i>Language and Learning, The Debate between Jean Piaget and Noam Chomsky</i>, Harvard University Press, Cambridge, MA, 1980.</li>
